When I‚Äôm not working on research or organizing beach cleanups, I‚Äôm usually hanging out with my kelp-obsessed dog, who thinks seaweed is the world‚Äôs best snack. We spend a lot of time at the beach (where else would we be?), and I‚Äôve learned more about marine ecosystems from her food preferences than from any textbook.


